Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request

Class ClassificationInferenceRequest

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request.ClassificationInferenceRequest
public class ClassificationInferenceRequest extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents a classification inference request in the Roboflow API.
This class is used to send a request to the Roboflow API to perform classification inference on an image, providing necessary parameters such as model ID, input image, preprocessing options, and more.

      A flag indicating whether the inference usage is billable.
      This field specifies whether the inference request will incur charges.
